.TH PHYSICS-SERVER 1 "2027-12-07" "Cohesix" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
physics-server \- process physics job files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B physics-server
.RI [--job-dir " dir"]
.RI [--sim-dir " dir"]
.RI [--log-file " file"]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B physics-server
watches a directory for
.B physics_job_*.json
files, runs simple simulations, and writes results under
.BR /sim .
Status is updated in
.B /srv/physics/status
and logs append to the specified file.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --job-dir
Directory containing job files (default "/mnt/physics_jobs").
.TP
.B --sim-dir
Output directory for world and result JSON (default "/sim").
.TP
.B --log-file
Path to the log file (default "/srv/trace/sim.log").
.SH EXAMPLES
.B physics-server --job-dir /mnt/jobs --sim-dir /sim
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR cohtrace (1)
